headline.main: Quebec Musher Collects 8th Win in Maine's Can-Am Crown
headline.print_headline: Quebec Musher Collects 8th Win in Maine's Can-Am Crown

lead_paragraph: A Quebec musher picked up his eighth victory in Maine's biggest sled dog race, finishing the truncated 250-mile Irving Woodlands Can-Am Crown 28 minutes ahead of his closest competitor.
